  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>You're in Hell - Now what?</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ricardo the chicken was sent to Hell for bad boy crimes <i>(being cool)</i>, and now he must find a way back to his world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3510020/extras/c638786033ad3a6de8487ab853dcbdcd.avif?t=1766966989\" width=616 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3510020/extras/bef3e9edd5695cbb75223dc8f94718b8.poster.avif?t=1766966989\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3510020/extras/bef3e9edd5695cbb75223dc8f94718b8.webm?t=1766966989\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Explore different landscapes</u></strong> in search of the Hell Bells, devices that open the exit!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3510020/extras/e9f15cbebd1e26020f485121d6e4d56f.avif?t=1766966989\" width=616 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3510020/extras/e6cf6d7b08bd35280c02656354ddcd6f.poster.avif?t=1766966989\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3510020/extras/e6cf6d7b08bd35280c02656354ddcd6f.webm?t=1766966989\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3510020/extras/e6cf6d7b08bd35280c02656354ddcd6f.mp4?t=1766966989\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Jump</u></strong> high, <u><strong>dash</strong></u> a lot, and <u><strong>grind</strong></u> icy rails! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grab <u><strong>powerups</strong></u> to improve your abilities - They provide Ricardo with <i>gnarly accessories</i> too!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3510020/extras/954df25325359ddea075be119c416bcb.avif?t=1766966989\" width=616 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3510020/extras/bf3b2c6334f33fa2ea39e588d21bcbaa.poster.avif?t=1766966989\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3510020/extras/bf3b2c6334f33fa2ea39e588d21bcbaa.webm?t=1766966989\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3510020/extras/bf3b2c6334f33fa2ea39e588d21bcbaa.mp4?t=1766966989\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Of course there are enemies. And lots of fire. <strong><u>This IS Hell</u></strong>, after all.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3510020/extras/65b453a169c2094e04252aac6f8d2746.avif?t=1766966989\" width=616 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Weird allies? Premonitions of disaster? No one seems to know for sure. <i><strong>They could be useful, though...</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Do you have what it takes to return home and take your life back?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Then stop the <u><strong>ultimate evil</strong></u> blocking your way!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3510020/extras/070c44dcf68b880c1b9980e2325ff439.avif?t=1766966989\" width=616 height=250 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>You're in Hell - Now what?</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ricardo the chicken was sent to Hell for bad boy crimes <i>(being cool)</i>, and now he must find a way back to his world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3510020/extras/c638786033ad3a6de8487ab853dcbdcd.avif?t=1766966989\" width=616 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3510020/extras/bef3e9edd5695cbb75223dc8f94718b8.poster.avif?t=1766966989\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3510020/extras/bef3e9edd5695cbb75223dc8f94718b8.webm?t=1766966989\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Explore different landscapes</u></strong> in search of the Hell Bells, devices that open the exit!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3510020/extras/e9f15cbebd1e26020f485121d6e4d56f.avif?t=1766966989\" width=616 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3510020/extras/e6cf6d7b08bd35280c02656354ddcd6f.poster.avif?t=1766966989\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3510020/extras/e6cf6d7b08bd35280c02656354ddcd6f.webm?t=1766966989\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3510020/extras/e6cf6d7b08bd35280c02656354ddcd6f.mp4?t=1766966989\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Jump</u></strong> high, <u><strong>dash</strong></u> a lot, and <u><strong>grind</strong></u> icy rails! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grab <u><strong>powerups</strong></u> to improve your abilities - They provide Ricardo with <i>gnarly accessories</i> too!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3510020/extras/954df25325359ddea075be119c416bcb.avif?t=1766966989\" width=616 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3510020/extras/bf3b2c6334f33fa2ea39e588d21bcbaa.poster.avif?t=1766966989\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3510020/extras/bf3b2c6334f33fa2ea39e588d21bcbaa.webm?t=1766966989\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3510020/extras/bf3b2c6334f33fa2ea39e588d21bcbaa.mp4?t=1766966989\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Of course there are enemies. And lots of fire. <strong><u>This IS Hell</u></strong>, after all.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3510020/extras/65b453a169c2094e04252aac6f8d2746.avif?t=1766966989\" width=616 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Weird allies? Premonitions of disaster? No one seems to know for sure. <i><strong>They could be useful, though...</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Do you have what it takes to return home and take your life back?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Then stop the <u><strong>ultimate evil</strong></u> blocking your way!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3510020/extras/070c44dcf68b880c1b9980e2325ff439.avif?t=1766966989\" width=616 height=250 /></span></p>",
